body:
This PR combines all L1T DQM developments up to 8_0_9, making cms-sw/cmssw#14463 obsolete and merging cms-sw/cmssw#14634. A corresponding PR for 8_1_X is in the works (timescale unknown).

@vanbesien, this should be safe to patch onto an 8_0_10 release online. It was a little slow to test from overseas, but the code compiles and runs in a fresh 8_0_9 release.

@mzarucki @EsmaeelEskandari @nhaubrich @nsmith-, Is it okay to consider this the final PR based on the 8_0_9 DQM development branch? If so, I'll create an 8_0_10 DQM development branch for us to work on.
